In this question we have to modify the given array such that all unique elements should be at front.
JAVA solution :- 
class Solution {
    public int removeDuplicates(int[] nums) {
        int k = nums.length;
        int i = 0, j = 1;
        while(j < nums.length) {
            if(nums[i] == nums[j]) {
                k--;
                j++;
            } else{
                nums[i+1] = nums[j];
                i++;
                ++j;
            }
        }
        return k;
    }
}

